Decoupled Encoder Process
phase A: balanced ViT forward
phase B: backbone fwd/bwd
phase C: ViT recompute + bwd
→ ~90% of text-only throughput" style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;fillColor=#fafafa;strokeColor=#bbbbbb;fontSize=10;align=left;verticalAlign=top;" vertex="1" parent="1">
